  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    StockHistory
    Defines the interface for the stock symbol history class.
    StockQuote

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PropertiesFileReader
    Reads a properties file from disk and loads into a Properties object
    Stock
    Stores stock related data.
    SymbolMap
    Provides a lookup mechanism for all known NASDAQ stock symbols.
    User
    Defines the user data.
    UserInfo
    Defines the additional user information.
    YahooStockHistory
    Defines the data and JSON properties for the Yahoo stock history.
    YahooStockQuote
    Defines the data and JSON properties for the Yahoo stock quote.
